V0302_01_00_00_0.text:
I'm ready to go!
Let's do this!

V0302_01_00_01_0.text: If you lose cuz you take me lightly, that's on you.

V0302_01_00_02_1.text: Because the real Duel begins before the Duel!

V0302_01_00_04_0.text: I need you to help me with my plans.

V0302_01_00_05_0.text: If you still think I'm just a kid, that's not smart.

V0302_01_00_07_1.text: I won't let you interfere with my brother's plans!

V0302_01_00_08_0.text: So you're the ones trying to wreck Duel Links!

V0302_01_00_09_0.text: If you mess with Seto, I'll mess with you!

V0302_05_00_00_0.text: A Duel's not over until it's over!

V0302_07_09_01_0.text: I'll flip over my Set card!

V0302_08_00_01_0.text:
Here's my Quick-Play Spell!
Silver's Cry!

V0302_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Dragon Revival Rhapsody!

V0302_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Spell!
The Melody of Awakening Dragon!

V0302_08_00_04_0.text:
I'll call a Dragon with this!
The Flute of Summoning Dragon!

V0302_08_00_05_0.text: I'll resurrect a Dragon using Return of the Dragon Lords!

V0302_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Draconnection!

V0302_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Dragon Shrine!

V0302_08_00_08_0.text:
This card'll do!
Bingo Machine, Go!!!

V0302_08_00_09_0.text:
Blue-Eyes!
Show 'em your power!
Burst Stream of Destruction!

V0302_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Dragon's Rebirth!

V0302_09_00_03_0.text:
Ha! Gotcha!
Decoy Dragon fooled ya!

V0302_09_00_04_0.text: Totem Dragon uses its effect from the Graveyard!

V0302_09_00_06_0.text: Keeper of the Shrine's effect activates!

V0302_09_00_08_0.text: The King of D.'s effect activates!

V0302_09_00_10_0.text: Dragon Spirit of White's effect activates!

V0302_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0302_13_00_07_0.text:
Just what I need!
Keeper of the Shrine!

V0302_13_00_08_0.text: I believe in ya, Dragonic Guard!

V0302_13_00_17_0.text: Help me like you help my big bro!

V0302_37_00_00_0.text: Three of the strongest dragons fuse together!

V0302_13_00_21_0.text:
Come on out!
Blue-Eyes Solid Dragon!

V0302_17_00_01_0.text: I attack you with my monster!

V0302_16_00_00_0.text: Looks like this Duel is over.

V0302_19_00_06_0.text: Go, Vanguard of the Dragon! Attack!

V0302_21_00_01_0.text: You don't look so tough now.

V0302_28_00_00_0.text: I'm busy running a company, so don't waste my time.

V0302_28_00_01_0.text: As KaibaCorp's VP, being a great Duelist is part of the job!

V0302_28_00_02_0.text: Your first mistake was thinking you could win easily.

V0302_28_00_03_1.text: I'm pretty good at Dueling too.

V0302_28_00_04_0.text:
Sorry, Yugi!
But I'm not the same ol' kid anymore!

V0302_28_00_05_0.text: Maybe you should go back to Dueling against preschoolers.

V0302_28_00_06_0.text: It's about time you stop treating me like a kid.

V0302_28_00_07_1.text: Maybe there's still a bug in the system...

V0302_28_00_08_1.text: We already have all the pieces we need to win!

V0302_28_00_10_0.text: Your weird powers don't work on us!

V0302_28_00_11_0.text: You thought you could run from Seto without one last Duel?

V0302_28_00_12_0.text:
How's that, big bro?
Pretty good, right?

V0302_29_00_00_0.text:
Argh!
I can't believe I made those mistakes!

V0302_29_00_02_0.text: I'm embarrassed to show my face to my brother...

V0302_29_00_03_0.text: I guess I was the one who was underestimating you.

V0302_29_00_04_0.text:
Wow...
You really are tough to beat, Yugi.

V0302_29_00_08_0.text:
Argh...
I hate that you're so good!

V0302_29_00_09_0.text: You really are the best, Seto!

V0302_33_00_01_0.text: I always have an ace up my sleeve!

V0302_30_00_00_0.text: Finally you're starting to look scared.

V0302_34_00_01_0.text: Didn't you know I have all the pieces to win?

V0302_34_00_02_0.text: You scared me there for a sec.

V0302_34_00_04_0.text: I can't take much more of this...

V0302_32_00_00_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links
My big bro created an awesome world!

V0302_32_00_01_0.text: Seto created Duel Links for Duelists worldwide to battle!

V0302_35_00_01_0.text: I won't need Seto's help this time!

V0302_36_00_00_0.text: It's all set up for you to take 'em down!

V0302_36_00_02_0.text: Argh... You gotta find a way outta this...
